{"tid":2049092,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"世上最民主自由最有錢既國家都支持港版國安法，犀利！","createTime":"2020-06-03T08:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T09:55:17.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc12009146a7b03cec87408bfafa26eaa7aa07a","tid":2049092,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:24:29.000Z","msg":"#UgandaForever 🙅🙅🙅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200603-0620copy_YC2fG_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200603-0620copy_YC2fG_1200x0.png&h=52d04311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大上星期通過決定，授權人大常委訂立港版國安法，引發國際社會關注；中國官媒《新華社》綜合多名駐外記者刊登報道，指「多國政府」支持人大訂立國安法，是中國內政別國無權干涉，報道列舉了朝鮮、斯里蘭卡、緬甸、菲律賓、敘利亞、坦桑尼亞、布隆迪、烏干達官員的發言。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述朝鮮外務省發言人指，完全支持中國「黨和政府」為維護國家主權與安全，維護領土完整與一國兩制、保障香港安定繁榮的措施，香港是中國領土不可分離的一部分，香港事務完全屬於中國內政，任何國家與勢力都無權說三道四；斯里蘭卡外交部長古納瓦德納則稱，支持中國捍衛領土主權和維護國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n而緬甸國際合作部長覺丁則指，緬方恪守一個中國原則，支持一國兩制，香港是中國不可分離的一部分，主權國家有權採取立法在內的預防性措施；菲律賓總統发言人哈里洛克則表示，香港事務完全是中國內政，菲律賓有數十萬公民在香港工作生活，相信持續繁榮穩定的香港將為菲律賓和菲律賓勞工帶來更多機會。<br />\n<br />\n另外，報道亦引述敘利亞外交部、坦桑尼亞政府首席發言人哈桑阿巴斯、布隆迪政府和烏干達政府发言人的表態，支持中國制訂港版國安法，香港是中國不可分離一部分，香港事務是中國內政不容其他國家干預等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BE-%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E5%88%97%E8%88%89-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93-%E6%95%98%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E-%E5%B8%83%E9%9A%86%E8%BF%AA-%E7%83%8F%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%94%E7%AD%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%2588%2589-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593-%25E6%2595%2598%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25BA%259E-%25E5%25B8%2583%25E9%259A%2586%25E8%25BF%25AA-%25E7%2583%258F%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E9%2581%2594%25E7%25AD%2589%2F&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BHr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=e404bad9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%2588%2589-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593-%25E6%2595%2598%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25BA%259E-%25E5%25B8%2583%25E9%259A%2586%25E8%25BF%25AA-%25E7%2583%258F%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E9%2581%2594%25E7%25AD%2589%2F&h=eb5df090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BE-%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E5%88%97%E8%88%89-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93-%E6%95%98%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E-%E5%B8%83%E9%9A%86%E8%BF%AA-%E7%83%8F%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%94%E7%AD%89/</a>"},{"pid":"dac608710fbdc293bb1527e0356e6bf0dd895fdf","tid":2049092,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"18個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7c6btcK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7c6btcK.png&h=48161e07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47ac25380ce0804cce89ddc2ac2d2082c1e7ed73","tid":2049092,"uid":137480,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"大哥普京點解唔出黎支持一下，習種要生氣氣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a65f350f93d20e8a2a17800166a3486769e24f","tid":2049092,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:26:55.000Z","msg":"Wakanda"},{"pid":"9df3412548abb60642a10d46c1c5457c810d2aed","tid":2049092,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47ac25380ce0804c